---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '9 April 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | FisherDigital"
  description="How FisherDigital collects, uses, and protects your personal data. Plain-English privacy policy for our website visitors and clients."
  schemaType="legal"
>
  <section class="section-light py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">

      <!-- Header -->
      <p class="label mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-4">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-12">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-base leading-relaxed">

        <!-- Intro -->
        <div>
          <p>
            This policy explains what personal data FisherDigital collects when you use our website
            (fisherdigital.co.uk), why we collect it, and what your rights are. We have kept it short
            and written in plain English because nobody should need a law degree to understand how
            their data is handled.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Who we are -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">Who we are</h2>
          <p>
            FisherDigital is a web design studio run by Joshua Fisher, based in Bristol, United Kingdom.
            When this policy says "we", "us", or "our", it means FisherDigital.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you have any questions about this policy or your data, you can reach us at
            <a href="mailto:fisherwebco@gmail.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">fisherwebco@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- What we collect -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">What data we collect</h2>
          <p>We only collect data that you give us directly or that is gathered automatically when you visit our site.</p>

          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-500 text-text mt-6 mb-2">Contact form submissions</h3>
          <p>
            When you fill in our contact form, we collect your name, email address, phone number (if provided),
            and message. This data is sent through Formspree, a third-party form handling service, and forwarded
            to our email inbox.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-500 text-text mt-6 mb-2">Analytics data</h3>
          <p>
            We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. This collects anonymised data like
            which pages you visit, how long you stay, and what device or browser you are using. Google Analytics
            uses cookies to do this. You can opt out by adjusting your browser's cookie settings or using
            Google's opt-out browser add-on.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-500 text-text mt-6 mb-2">What we do not collect</h3>
          <p>
            We do not collect payment card details directly. All payments are handled securely by Stripe.
            We do not buy, scrape, or otherwise acquire personal data from third parties.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- How we use it -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">How we use your data</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
            <li>To respond to your enquiry when you submit a contact form.</li>
            <li>To send you information about our services if you have asked us to.</li>
            <li>To understand how our website is used so we can improve it.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            We will never sell your data to anyone. We will never send you marketing emails unless you
            have specifically asked to hear from us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Third parties -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">Third parties</h2>
          <p>We share data with a small number of services that help us run the site.</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3 text-text-secondary">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-text">Formspree</strong> processes contact form submissions on our behalf.
              Their privacy policy is at
              <a href="https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy</a>.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-text">Google Analytics</strong> collects anonymised usage data.
              Google's privacy policy is at
              <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">policies.google.com/privacy</a>.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-text">Stripe</strong> handles payment processing for our services.
              Their privacy policy is at
              <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">stripe.com/privacy</a>.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            We do not share your personal data with anyone else unless required to by law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Your rights -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">Your rights under UK GDPR</h2>
          <p>
            Under the UK General Data Protection Regulation, you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3 text-text-secondary">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li>Ask us to correct any data that is inaccurate.</li>
            <li>Ask us to delete your data.</li>
            <li>Object to us processing your data.</li>
            <li>Request a copy of your data in a portable format.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            To exercise any of these rights, email us at
            <a href="mailto:fisherwebco@gmail.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">fisherwebco@gmail.com</a>.
            We will respond within 30 days.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you are not satisfied with our response, you can lodge a complaint with the
            <a href="https://ico.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">Information Commissioner's Office (ICO)</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Data retention -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">How long we keep your data</h2>
          <p>
            Contact form submissions are kept for as long as needed to deal with your enquiry and
            any resulting work. If you become a client, we retain your project data for the duration
            of our working relationship and a reasonable period afterwards for our records.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You can ask us to delete your data at any time by emailing
            <a href="mailto:fisherwebco@gmail.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">fisherwebco@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Cookies -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Our site uses a small number of cookies, primarily for analytics. For full details,
            see our <a href="/cookies/" class="text-accent hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Changes -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we will update the "last updated"
            date at the top. We encourage you to check back occasionally.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-border">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-600 tracking-tight text-text mb-3">Get in touch</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, contact us at:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 text-text-secondary">
            <p>FisherDigital</p>
            <p>Bristol, United Kingdom</p>
            <p>
              <a href="mailto:fisherwebco@gmail.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">fisherwebco@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
